Somfy InteO is a complete plug-and-play home automation system with the primary goal of caring for the family. It is a solution that allows you to control lights, motorized curtains, and monitor all the doors and windows in your house.

Through the Somfy InteO, you can control and create scenes for your curtains and blinds equipped with Somfy motors.

By enabling the Somfy InteO skill, you synchronize the devices and scenes created in the InteO app with Alexa, gaining even more freedom!

To make use of this, you'll need to connect Alexa to your Somfy products following these simple steps:

01 - Download the "InteO" app from your app store;
02 - Register your Inteo account using an email address;
03 - Sync your InteO;
04 - Configure your devices (curtains and blinds);
05 - Create scenes for your devices;
06 - Search for the "Somfy InteO" skill in the Alexa app;
07 - Click "Enable for Use," and you'll be redirected to the login screen;
08 - Enter your account information and password.
09 - Done! The configuration is complete.

It's not necessary to open the Somfy InteO app to operate your home devices; just say: Alexa.

Try saying:
"Alexa, open the blinds."
"Alexa, close the curtain."

Learn more about Somfy: https://www.somfy.com
